{"tid":1802064,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請棄用送頭一詞","createTime":"2019-12-29T06:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T16:09:08.000Z","uid":89974,"like":49,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"14e50ae993c63a4e076b006bf4eb62f85f8b5534","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"【唔做當然唔錯 暖氣絕無送頭】<br />\n<br />\n請棄用送頭一詞。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.#損失係無可避免</span></span><br />\n當三權分立、警權無限膨脹，香港人係無智取或者靜靜地贏嘅空間。因為硬擋而招致嘅濫捕、私刑、冤獄甚至謀殺，係難以全面迴避嘅成本。<br />\n同樣道理，抗爭時間表亦係不得不用。每次抗爭降溫就必有搜捕清算，而香港人唔係軍隊，現階段要聚到人保持溫度就只有時間表呢張開口牌。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲不利嘅因素，係抗爭必然嘅成本。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.#唔好忽視無形成果</span></span><br />\n「送頭」係建基於打機只有一時成敗嘅描述。現實中即使呢一刻睇唔到明顯嘅傷害，手足嘅行動同樣會對敵方造成壓力、為其他人作為行動參考，以及創造衝破膠著狀況嘅可能性。<br />\n就等於和你shop靠時間表成事，即使被捕者眾，但佢對商場嘅打擊、逼使敵軍進一步破壞規範行動，都係輸出嘅一種。<br />\n<br />\n有輸出就唔係送頭。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.#切勿因為愧疚叫停</span></span><br />\n一靜，就有手足被搜捕被消失。香港自六月以嚟只有每況愈下，「不送頭」事事迴避，只係對凶險現況掩耳盜鈴。<br />\n因為良心不安叫停活動，就同叫陣地戰中守衛前線嘅手足快啲走一樣，都係忽視咗佢地正喺度為我地buy time嘅事實。<br />\n係，我理解目睹手足受苦有幾心痛愧疚，但從來愧疚只有一個方法解決：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">用你相信嘅方法取勝，把握每一分秒做正事。</span><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4.#送頭指控係極端侮辱</span></span><br />\n既然損失無法避免、行動又永遠唔會無成果，手足嘅損失就絕唔能夠話係送頭。<br />\n因為咁樣講，你係嘲笑緊手足嘅判斷，侮辱緊手足嘅付出。<br />\n當手足迎難以上嘅時候，暖氣軍師高高在上訓斥佢送頭，只係繼警暴後對手足造成二次傷害，只係落井下石嘅風涼話。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">畢竟最大嘅送頭，就係喺半年前612開始，我地決定反抗極權。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14jBscL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14jBscL.jpg&h=ee44e6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：勇武香港 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Syzuk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Syzuk7&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK94tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=1490f944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Syzuk7</a>"},{"pid":"d1643bf60a326804282626ab1dd18ce4877f6d52","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:52:01.000Z","msg":"有手足肯做野仲要俾人笑係送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b850c1c6a17f7721354284335c3fd436d0b41aeb","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70007944bdda6650dee87e57d6a8a4e23269e3b0","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3094e83299baac0715004164b5090bf593b6326","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572f09e1e8b7785673057fc81ea0679c6faabc45","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2da5336a64c6d7d2990cb15573a52a7373c23a0","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e7f6c96fda1a978700629f4317500efc3e8fc9","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed19119e34ca990a3a6b8323cb3651f1b443c74","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0b0ae357eabb4188c2ed57869dfd02370e6e70","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1451aed66a0ab50fa1e0ddb5c41ea9e230cb004a","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac328fed7fe957cb6a58eca9618da17347623da","tid":1802064,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c60b1bddca05c26466d82185d013d5284e9ce96","tid":1802064,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc9036fe2df1b75bc829810b577badaf8343629","tid":1802064,"uid":306621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"其實講得送頭呢2個字<br />\n9成9係冷氣軍師/花生友<br />\n明明大家係手足，會屌鳩自己友比人拉?<br />\n手足，係自己既手/足，點解要屌自己友，真係唔撚明"},{"pid":"c8b21ed1cc4ac3980e2ce7a6175875e591f57579","tid":1802064,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"講真係要做軍師就唔係盲目叫人唔好做乜,而係教手足點樣可糸1降低行動風險,係咁話人送頭叫人唔好再做果啲根本係將手足嘅犧牲白費"},{"pid":"bb788b5e5d15a9cb8e98aa60ff11f94872a607c2","tid":1802064,"uid":310534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"啱，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b059c999aed1fe60aeccaa7f3ddebe9c95ca59dd","tid":1802064,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCjedYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCjedYt.jpg&h=f54b7067&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4b76b9d3f1fa07d2a47137c6ce2fae04bbd0f9e","tid":1802064,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n12.31 和你拖<br />\n12.31 和你shop<br />\n12.31 和你倒數<br />\n1.1 兩點維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">*請準時 勿打尖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中環pepe專門店=人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QT3yuw6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQT3yuw6.jpg&h=0751f16c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OXZ3cu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OXZ3cu.jpg&h=c669060e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/858eR5P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F858eR5P.jpg&h=68a0eac8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LaW8b5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLaW8b5Q.jpg&h=1fe56a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCWgkZa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCWgkZa.jpg&h=f4098c92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xV7CPSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxV7CPSw.jpg&h=5ea23210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uz7rJc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUz7rJc9.jpg&h=c6b65d6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef89a43fccd34cf629c56b41676999358107aaf","tid":1802064,"uid":182197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"對暖氣軍師黎講<br />\n出黎=送頭<br />\n唔送頭的方法=係屋企坐係電腦到打報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edf1d8091e7cb7f25ddfe2d2e33b0e9edf5940b","tid":1802064,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep